{"id":"234810388_Factoring_and_decomposing_Ore_polynomials_over","abstract":"We present algorithms for computing factorizations and least common left multiple (LCLM) decompositions of Ore polynomials over Fq(t), for a prime power q=pμ. Our algorithms are effective in Fq(t)[D; σ,δ], for any automorphism σ and σ-derivation δ of Fq(t). On input f ∈ Fq(t)[D;σ,δ], the algorithms run in time polynomial in degD(f), degt(f), p and μ.","authors":["Mark Giesbrecht","Yang Zhang"],"meta":["August 2003","DOI:10.1145/860854.860888"],"references":["295214210_On_ore_rings_linear_operators_and_factorization","267334617_Free_Rings_and_their_Relations","266513044_On_Ore_rings_linear_operators_and_factorization","265896089_Differential_equations_in_characteristic_p","265366755_Skew_fields_Theory_of_general_division_rings","265366672_Reduction_modulo_p_of_differential_equations","256336319_Decomposition_of_algebras_over_F_q_X_1_X_m","248556638_Fixed_Rings_of_Finite_Automorphism_Groups_of_Associative_Rings","246995074_On_a_Special_Class_of_Polynomials","245790634_Contributions_to_the_Theory_of_Finite_Fields","242637210_Formale_Theorie_der_linearen_Differentialgleichungen_Zweiter_Teil","242619135_Theory_of_Non-Commutative_Polynomials","238674158_Modular_methods_for_factoring_differential_operators","225696009_Smash_products_and_outer_derivations","225212388_Die_Irreducibilitt_der_homogenen_linearen_Differentialgleichungen"]}